#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:1
msgid "Add missing selection mode behavior in parallel coordinates chart"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:3
msgid ""
"The parallel coordinates chart supports new keyboard shortcuts for different "
"selection modes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:4
msgid "Press `Ctrl` while selecting to add to the current selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:5
msgid "Press `Shift` while selecting to substract from the current selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:6
msgid ""
"Press `Ctrl+Shift` while selecting to toggle compared to the current "
"selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/add-missing-selection-behavior-parallel-coordinates-view.md:8
msgid ""
"As `GetMouseSelectionMode` function is now used by both `vtkChartXY` and "
"`vtkChartParallelCoordinates`, it has now been moved to the parent class "
"`vtkChart`. The static function with the same logic is now called "
"`GetSelectionModeFromMouseModifiers`. Moreover, `vtkChartXY::"
"GetMouseSelectionMode` is now deprecated."
msgstr ""
